One of your team members is about to advance to level <5+>. In order for you to be eligible to receive contributions from team members advancing to level <5+> you must be at level <5+> or greater. Level <5+> contributions are directed to Level <5+> members or greater. To advance to level <5+> Click the Advance to level <5+> link. If you are not at level <5+> when one of your team members pays to advance to level <5+>, you will not be included as one of the payees. All level <5+> contributions are $100.

